{"tid":2318200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趙斗淳大後日出獄丨《許願》原型強姦犯提交過百請願書 懇求與受害人見面","createTime":"2020-12-09T07:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T09:29:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69104b4b7ddf92d2191c10a0fb5b5f9f1a3e0301","tid":2318200,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"聲稱忘記犯罪情況<br />\n趙斗淳將於大後日（12日）出獄，近日他再次成為新聞人物，根據韓媒JTBC新聞報道，趙斗淳在獄中曾多次寫下請願書，除了聲稱不記得當時的犯罪情況外，更揚言希望與受害人見面。據報道指，趙斗淳在請願書中雖然指罪名「太丟臉」，所以在獄中一次也沒有向其他獄友透露。而趙斗淳入獄後曾提交超過100個請願書，當中他很多時結尾都會拜託要求與受害人見面。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201209/W6CG3C6LUNAJRL3ROH7HN4M4SI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201209%2FW6CG3C6LUNAJRL3ROH7HN4M4SI%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=57f0a847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201209%2FW6CG3C6LUNAJRL3ROH7HN4M4SI%2F&h=f6e74ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201209/W6CG3C6LUNAJRL3ROH7HN4M4SI/</a>"},{"pid":"0cab457aa65f036cd3f4e076c478d714241ae09c","tid":2318200,"uid":78349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"而家個個都帶口罩<br />\n放返出黎都認唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc72dab7538ce62fa409f7c68cb0dcdf904a4fc","tid":2318200,"uid":73366,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖 見有報導講其他犯話佢喺監倉都性慾好強 咩見到cctv對啲電波有性慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話佢可以連續一個鐘做1000下掌上壓 好心就捉佢入精神病院 唔好放返出嚟"},{"pid":"ebdd612b0267e5bc54f8e357d10a0a00ae7befc9","tid":2318200,"uid":10241,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"佢同佢老婆兩個都癡線<br />\n咬住個受害人唔放<br />\n人地成家搬左佢老婆又搬去附近<br />\n又話係人地屋企附近開舖<br />\n依家又話佢想同受害人見面<br />\n唔應該放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif