s/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"咁都放得出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n距離趙斗淳出獄之日不到一週，不只南韓人心惶惶，連獄友A也爆料趙斗淳的近況，獄友A指出 :「他的身體條件彷彿只有30歲，體能遠超許多年輕人。有健身教練更表示，趙斗淳的體力、肌肉和耐力可以說不亞於專業選手。」趙斗淳則對獄友A聲稱 :「趙鍛煉身體是因為擔心出獄後會遭到報復，避免被市民使用私刑。」<br />\n<br />\n獄友A透露，以自己與其同住的經歷來看，趙斗淳在獄中絕對從來沒有反省過。因此在服刑期間，其他囚犯都對趙斗淳避而遠之，<span class=\"red\">而且在心理課程的輔導下，他仍然具有暴力傾向。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/newtalk.tw/news/view/amp/2020-12-08/505683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Famp%2F2020-12-08%2F505683&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=5ed9d5e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/newtalk.tw/news/view/amp/2020-12-08/505683</a>"},{"pid":"6804ea26761a9e03982802fb5c56286c30c0a907","tid":2318200,"uid":2914,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"放佢出黎咪搵人打佢囉<br />\n你驚都無用嫁<br />\n想保護受害者或家人就係咁"},{"pid":"84298c664eda5975e11ba074f90e6ab77d65d5d5","tid":2318200,"uid":64619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"閹左佢啦屌"},{"pid":"c21dde663271a03075a4ead48b57ac0716cc3498","tid":2318200,"uid":212274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6804ea26761a9e03982802fb5c56286c30c0a907","tid":2318200,"uid":2914,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"放佢出黎咪搵人打佢囉<br />\n你驚都無用嫁<br />\n想保護受害者或家人就係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:33:20.000Z","msg":"你搵人打佢，激嬲佢搵你報仇仲驚，殺你全家都似<br />\n<br />\n南韓d男人好似好多暴力案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b28eb9579645d1dc65e80aea32be1e6d4cb298b","tid":2318200,"uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6a92b1378dd30cd2f49a69eb70623954169278d0","tid":2318200,"uid":73366,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"qu